name: PerformanceTiming.domContentLoadedEventEnd
description: The legacy PerformanceTiming.domContentLoadedEventEnd read-only property returns an unsigned long long representing the moment, in milliseconds since the UNIX epoch, right after all the scripts that need to be executed as soon as possible, in order or not, has been executed.
